some ships still anchor off-shore toward the southeast side of the island and tender guests to shore. modest-sized ships can choose to dock at the port of benoa not far from denpasar, kuta and sanur. the dock area is basically industrial, with few amenities and no atms, but masses of taxis are usually ready to whisk you to nearby destinations at a moderate cost. get around[edit] kecak dance performance at uluwatu bali is a fairly large island and you will need a method to get around if you plan on exploring more than the hotel pool. rapid, seemingly uncontrolled development 